Data Discovery

We are sure that new discovery techniques and data aggregation algorithms are real enablers to face new challenges to come.

Map Lovers

Since digital world interconnects real world and we don't live in Pangea, maps are our best allies to make the information more comprehensive.

Heuristic

We love heuristic analysis. We use all the information collected to make inferences and find useful relationships that allow us to understand the digital world.

Creative Commons

The world is full of information thanks to people is sharing it. Keep your mind open.

Relationship Focused

It's time to embrace new graph-based technologies as this ever-more-connected world keeps growing and data relationships are key to understand it.

ENHANCE

Increase your analysis and survey capabilities through an incredible and powerful source of data about systems and networks connections.

ADAPT

Change the way you look at how services are exposed to attacks in internet. Discover the new connectivity paradigm and adapt your security policies.

REACT

Enrich your cyber-intelligence analytics. Be prepared for the new ecosystem composed by new technologies and protocols. Attackers are looking at your, you cannot afford to be left behind.

description:
RESTFull API to get data from MrLooquer service. MrLooquer combines open source intelligence techniques with heuristic and
data mining to perform one of the first attempts to create a real map about
IPv6 deployment and its relationship with current networks and protocols.
